article.description: — Jeenathan Williams had 21 points as Buffalo romped past Miami (Ohio) 90-62 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Williams scores 21 to carry Buffalo over Miami (Ohio) 90-62
article.linkText: Williams scores 21 to carry Buffalo over Miami (Ohio) 90-62
article.story: OXFORD, Ohio -- — Jeenathan Williams had 21 points as Buffalo romped past Miami (Ohio) 90-62 on Tuesday. Jayvon Graves had 13 points and seven rebounds for Buffalo (3-2, 1-1 Mid-American Conference). David Nickelberry added 12 points. Isaiah Coleman-Lands had 12 points for the RedHawks (3-2, 0-1). Mekhi Lairy added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
